@@ -0,0 +1,11 @@
+% 迭代输出函数
+function status = myOutputFcn(t, y, flag)
+    if strcmp(flag, 'init')
+        fprintf('Simulation started.\n');
+    elseif strcmp(flag, '')
+        fprintf('At time %.2f \n', t);
+    elseif strcmp(flag, 'done')
+        fprintf('Simulation finished.\n');
+    end
+    status = [];
+end
\ No newline at end of file

Index:

+++ 
@@ -0,0 +1,13 @@
+
+function status = myOutputFcn(t, y, flag)
+    global shouldStop;  % 使用全局变量
+    if strcmp(flag, 'init')
+        fprintf('Simulation started.\n');
+    elseif strcmp(flag, 'done')
+        fprintf('Simulation finished.\n');
+        shouldStop = true;  % 设置全局变量，跳出 while 循环
+    elseif strcmp(flag, '')
+        fprintf('At time %.2f \n', t);
+    end
+    status = [];
+end
\ No newline at end of file
